&lt;p&gt;Whittington Health Trust are looking for Registered Mental Health Nurses with experience working in a Mental Health environment to join their team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Required Skills and Experience;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Registered Mental Health Nurse- RMN&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working within a Mental Health ward/hospital within the last 3 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NMC registration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent communication skills, both written and verbal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;6 Months NHS experience within the last 3 years&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Nurses are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Priority of shifts over an agency worker, accommodating your availability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated recruitment team to ensure you can work as quickly as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated compliance team that ensures you remain compliant to work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Core skills training&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested in this position please apply online.&lt;/p&gt;
